<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Tradeboard</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #8B5CF6;
            --primary-light: #EDE9FE;
            --text-dark: #1F2937;
            --text-light: #6B7280;
            --accent-color: #7C3AED;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 25%, var(--accent-color) 100%);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        .welcome-message {
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .name {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .name::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .role-section {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .support-message {
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding: 16px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(10px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .animate {
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out forwards;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container animate">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Tradeboard</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <p>Hello {{partnerName}},</p>
                <p>You have been added as an accountability partner for <span class="name">{{userName}}</span> in their
                    trading journey with Tradeboard.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="role-section">
                <p>As an accountability partner, you will receive {{frequency}} updates on <span
                        class="name">{{userName}}</span>'s trading performance. These updates will help you support and
                    encourage <span class="name">{{userName}}</span> in their trading goals.</p>
            </div>

            <p>Your role as an accountability partner is crucial in helping traders stay motivated and disciplined. We
                appreciate your commitment to supporting <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>.</p>

            <div class="support-message">
                <p>If you have any questions about your role or the updates you'll receive, please don't hesitate to
                    reach out to us.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Thank you for being a part of the Tradeboard community!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>